    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Grid convergence is well-characterized, output comparison errors are within acceptance bounds across all operating points, and the validation activities are directly relevant to the CPB COU. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
